From 0000000000000000000000000000000000000000 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Entrpi <entrpi@proton.me>
Date: Mon, 16 Feb 2026 17:27:21 +1100
Subject: [PATCH] arm64: dts: cix: Add Sky1 SoC and board device trees

Add comprehensive device tree support for CIX Sky1 SoC including:
- sky1.dtsi: Full SoC description with all peripherals
- sky1-orion-o6.dts: Radxa Orion O6 board
- sky1-orion-o6n.dts: Radxa Orion O6N board
- sky1-orangepi-6-plus.dts: Orange Pi 6 Plus board
- dt-bindings headers for clocks, resets, pins, power, thermal

Extends upstream base DTS with USB, display, audio, network,
GPIO, thermal zones, and board-specific peripheral enablement.
